item.title: Relaunch of Herbert Mühlburger’s Weblog
item.description: These days I decided to relaunch my weblog. Due to a problem in the wordpress upgrade process I was forced to this decision. The language of my weblog will now switch to English as well. As you may have recognized my weblog is updated in the visual manner as well. Hope to enlarge the number of my readers and to interest new people in my posts.
